flowchart TD

    A[User Opens Template Designer] --> B{Select Database Source}

    B -->|Hosted PostgreSQL| C[Enter PostgreSQL Connection URL]
    B -->|Local PostgreSQL| D[Use Local Connection]

    C --> E[Validate Connection]
    D --> E

    E -->|Success| F[Read Database Metadata]
    E -->|Failed| G[Show Connection Error]

    F --> H[Fetch Tables]
    F --> I[Fetch Columns]
    F --> J[Fetch Primary Keys]
    F --> K[Fetch Foreign Keys / Relationships]

    H --> L[Build Database Model]
    I --> L
    J --> L
    K --> L

    L --> M[Display Visual Schema]

    M --> N[Show Tables]
    N --> O[
    Example

    Customer
    • customer_id
    • name
    • email

    Orders
    • order_id
    • customer_id
    • amount
    ]

    L --> P[Display Relationship Lines]

    O --> Q[User Selects Columns]
    P --> Q

    Q --> R{Selection Valid?}

    R -->|No| S[Highlight Invalid Join or Constraint]
    S --> Q

    R -->|Yes| T[Build Template Configuration]

    T --> U[Optional Filters]
    U --> V[Optional Sorting]
    V --> W[Optional Grouping]

    W --> X[Submit Template Definition]

    X --> Y[Backend API]

    subgraph Backend
        Y --> Z[Validate Metadata]
        Z --> AA[Generate Required JOINs]
        AA --> AB[Generate SQL Query]
        AB --> AC[Store Template]
    end

    AC --> AD[Template Ready for Report Generation]